+//! APIs, verifying the full JS → Rust pipeline for:
+//! - `pi.sendMessage()` / `pi.sendUserMessage()`
+//! - `pi.events("appendEntry", ...)` / session metadata
+//! - Tool management (`setActiveTools`, `getActiveTools`, `getAllTools`)
